name: Expecto Patronum
description:
"Think of the happiest moment in your whole life".

These come as a set of both drawings.

This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Custom Design / Drawing / Tattoo.
description:
After much feedback and a multitude of requests, I've decided to put this as an option instore, to not only save run around for both you and myself, but also make it much easier.

Contact me via the link with what you would like drawn, and I will email you back and organise exactly what you would like as soon as possible.

The $50 is negotiable, depending on what the actual request is. But this can be discussed through the email correspondence.

name: Float
description: Throw caution to the wind, Give yourself to the sea. For the dangers beneath, Are not important to you or me. This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Blind Faith
description: We as a race are blind. In love, in faith, in fury. The heart and the head will forever be enemies, With the eyes telling lies to them both. This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Conviction
description: And with blood on your hands, Stand tall against your enemies, As underneath your cold glare and bitter words, Their defences will crumble. You will be free from their poisonous hands, And toxic slander, someday, someday. This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Metatron's Cube Print Skull
description:
This is a genuine ram / ewe skull, with a hand drawn Metatron's Cube on the top. Perfect for any spell work, altar or even bookshelf, this will be sure to add both a spiritual atmosphere to your space, and be a perfect adornment to any magickal area you have built. Metatron's Cube is a modern New Age name for a geometric figure composed of 13 equal circles with lines from the center of each circle extending out to the centers of the other 12 circles. Metatrons Cube is also known as "The Fruit of Life"

The name of Metatron's Cube makes reference to Metatron, an angel mentioned in apocryphal texts including the Second Book of Enoch and the Book of the Palaces. These texts rank Metatron second only to the Abrahamic God in the hierarchy of spiritual beings. The derivation of Metatron's cube from the tree of life, which the Talmud clearly states was excluded from human experience during the exile from Eden, has led some scholars to portray Metatron as the means by which humanity was given knowledge of YHVH; presumably implying that study of Metatron's cube would be necessary to understanding the tree of life.

Please note, as with any bone products, particular care is taken to keep it in next to pristine condition. Once your item has arrived, it is suitable to keep it out of direct sunlight for extended periods of time. The bone has been treated, however is still subject to fading and cracking if not cared for properly. With proper attention and care, this will be an eternally lasting curio for you to enjoy.

name: In Too Deep
description: And in the depths of hell, The monsters of dreary and gloom reside. Dragging us down into their watery graves, To feast on our hearts. Will you jump in with eyes closed, Or face the horrors to come? This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Knight Owl
description:
Alas, how the angels of ancient times whisper in our ears, While silently stalking, the mistakes of our past slip into our minds. There will be no saviours when time comes for absolution. Just the bitter cold, and the feathered touch of cruelty. Hold fast in your fruits of life, For the trees have withered and the horizon is tinted crimson and gold.
 This print is A3 sized, on medium stiffness, high quality card.

name: Ivory
description: Majestic, the bitter cold of reality, As we sell our souls for the materialistic pleasures. Surround ourselves in the very blood of those we walk on, Whilst the world around us burns in spite. This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Dizzy
description: Reverie and dizzy, we spin until the lights and stars join together in a maze of fire beneath our eyelids. This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Wishes Do Come True
description: And with but the cutest smile, Prettiest dress, And highest of hopes. The beaten and battered among us, Can achieve their hearts desire, If they wish, oh, but a wish. This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Vorpal
description: One, two! One, two! And through and through, The vorpal blade went snicker-snack! He left it dead, and with its head, He went galumphing back! This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Round The Twist
description: Have you ever.. Ever felt like this? Do strange things happen? Are you going, Round The Twist? This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Pentagram of Solomon Print Skull
description:
Hand drawn, this Tetragrammaton Print Skull is a must have for anyone involved in the goetia or the works of Crowley. Particularly useful in summoning, the rune marked pentagram, known specifically as the Tetragrammaton is used when evoking the Spirits of the Goetia, to preserve oneself from danger, and also allow the summoner to command said Goetic Spirits.

The bone has been treated, however is still subject to fading and cracking if not cared for properly. With proper attention and care, this will be an eternally lasting curio for you to enjoy.

name: Odonata Kismet
description:
Flickering through the sky like a reverie, Briefly perching twixt nebulae and galaxy, The dragonflies of the night will dot the sky like stars. Aurorae of wishes, Whispers spread across the wind. Faded lullabies create an ocean of dreams.
 This print is 25cm x 25cm, on medium stiffness, high quality card.

name: Kheper
description:
"Kheper-i kheper kheperu, kheper-kuy, M kheper n khepri kheperu m sep tepy". "I became, and the becoming became. I became by becoming the form of Khepra, god of transformations, who came into being the First Time. Through me all transformations were enacted."
This print is A3 sized, on medium stiffness, high quality card.

name: A New World, Reborn in Fire.
description:
Lo, each day become like a phoenix, Mortality in fire, rebirth in ash. Horizons tinted with gold and crimson, Be a new day, beginning. Twixt night and the end, my heart burns, The eyes of the covenant bathe all in the blood of rebirth, And the world will question itself. "Do we merely overlook the truth, when will we truly be able to see?"
This print is A3 sized, on medium stiffness, high quality card.

name: Fairytale
description:
<i>Alas, in a sculpted world of faeries, fiction and phantasmagoria,
Be there no harsher reality than the feeling of nostalgia.
Remembering what once was, and what will never be again,
Take me back, take me back.
To the sounds of children's laughter and sunnier skies,
O, how the world ahead looks darker,
Whilst the world behind looks brighter.
I will be a slave to my own memories,
For just one trip back.<i>

This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Memento Mortis
description: Be a deserted island, be isolated in the middle of the sea. Current, undertow, be swept away martyr, your belief in yourself is dithering. The things you cry out for nonchalantly, optimistically, hopefully... How they flee from your reaching fingers, cry, cry, wail.. oh wail. Too afraid to stretch, only within grasp will you venture? Do you feel the icy cold grip of the end? The frostbite is creeping over your flesh, And all you can do is watch as your heart turns to crystal. This print is A3 sized, and printed on high quality, medium stiffness card.

name: Love Letters
description:
Twixt your memories, there I reside, there I reside. Like a splinter from a sycamore amongst your twisted, gnarled ash. I hold you close as an evergreen, foliage in my head as pretty as your face. Existential quandaries pushing further into the cavern. Won't you hold my torch? Won't you hold my torch, please?
This print is A3 sized, on medium stiffness, high quality card.

name: Draconis Abhorae
description:
Writhing in the zephyrs of a salty sky, Dissonance of screaming, dreaming, wishing, whispers and sighs. The smell of death and romance lingers behind him, As if he wears it like a cologne. A thousand ghosts, play acrobat on his shoulders, haunted and haunting. The dragon who lives like a poltergeist, Spectral divination of the thoughts that surround him.
This print is A3 sized, and printed on medium stiffness, high quality card.
